  • Packages that use VectorMetadata 
    Package Description
    com.ojcoleman.europa.algos.vector
    Contains classes for genotypes that are constructed from genes and alleles that comprise a vector of double values.

      Methods in com.ojcoleman.europa.algos.vector that return VectorMetadata 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      VectorMetadata ParametrisedGeneType.getParamsAllele()
      The available parameters, and associated properties, whose value is an allele and so may change after this type of gene is added.
      VectorMetadata ParametrisedGeneType.getParamsGene()
      The available parameters, and associated properties, whose values should be fixed when a gene of this type is added.
      VectorMetadata ParametrisedGeneType.getParamsType()
      Similar to ParametrisedGeneType.getParamsGene(), however the parameters specified here are intended to be referenced from other genes or alleles (see ParametrisedGeneType.paramsTypeReference), instead of those parameters being set or evolved individually in each gene or allele.
